# Naming Conventions

- **PowerShell (`.ps1`)**: Use `PascalCase.ps1`.
- **Bash (`.sh`)**: Always use snake_case for shell scripts `lower_case_with_underscores.sh`.
- **Markdown (`.md`)**: Use `lower-case-with-dashes.md`, with the exception of `README.md`.
